author: Fearless & Far
description:
I just didn’t want that life anymore 👇

I don’t think we talk enough about how valid that sentence is. Sometimes you hit a point where staying the same feels heavier than changing.

Years ago I was scared of leaving my hometown, scared of cameras, scared of everything. But one day that line popped into my head… and I booked a one-way ticket.

Your whole life can shift from one honest thought. If something feels “not for you” anymore, that’s your sign to build a life that is.
